{"tid":2452091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拜登籲難民不要赴美 曾承諾放寬限制引發邊境危機 共和黨人：是他一手造成","createTime":"2021-03-18T14:58:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T16:43:01.000Z","uid":50386,"like":38,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"33841c921f8395efd8b91523c6c4c2b0842f1372","tid":2452091,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T14:58:47.000Z","msg":"美國總統拜登曾承諾放寬前任特朗普收緊的庇護政策，接收更多難民，導致邊境湧入中南美洲難民急增，其中包括數以千計無人陪伴的孩童，預料今年將是近20年來最多難民赴美的一年。然而邊境收容所人滿為患，生活條件惡劣，<span class=\"red\">拜登接受美國廣播公司（ABC）專訪時就呼籲難民「不要來美國」。</span><br />\n<br />\n拜登被問有關難民問題，他直言：「我可以很清楚地說，不要來了。不要離開你的城鎮、城市或社區。」對於被指放棄特朗普在議題上的強硬立場，是否變相鼓勵了這波移民潮，他稱2019年及2020年皆看到人數急增，而「這情況可能會惡化」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210318/EZN6VTTFCRDOPOCW7EIVPIWAEI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210318%2FEZN6VTTFCRDOPOCW7EIVPIWAEI%2F&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSrY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=a2cc86e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210318%2FEZN6VTTFCRDOPOCW7EIVPIWAEI%2F&h=a649f0c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210318/EZN6VTTFCRDOPOCW7EIVPIWAEI/</a>"},{"pid":"7437e20146313b7fa79777e0ca2d5650dbae6f00","tid":2452091,"uid":20870,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T15:00:37.000Z","msg":"呃完班左膠就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用完既棄係咩啊"},{"pid":"49d0fe7b12d3409ba7ff95a91d4e3b712717dd64","tid":2452091,"uid":37375,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T15:01:27.000Z","msg":"sounds good"},{"pid":"68c18b68ba1fff6ae10aa259467c5b70944b350a","tid":2452091,"uid":28114,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"49d0fe7b12d3409ba7ff95a91d4e3b712717dd64","tid":2452091,"uid":37375,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T15:01:27.000Z","msg":"sounds good"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T15:21:39.000Z","m